    <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
    <p>The Young Adult Ministry's purpose is to encourage and support young adults (ages 18-30) in their spiritual growth by:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Helping them come to Christ.</li>
        <li>Helping them to stay focused in the ways of Christ.</li>
        <li>Helping them to consider building an intimate relationship with Christ.</li>
        <li>Encouraging Spiritual and Educational growth through Bible study, prayer, and worship.</li>
        <li>Encouraging Stewardship growth - using their time, talents, and treasure for Christ.</li>
        <li>Encouraging Financial growth - tithes and offerings.</li>
        <li>Fostering Social growth through attending church, fellowship, and fostering independence.</li>
        <li>Praying on, depending on, and acting on, the Word of God.</li>
        <li>Encouraging and supporting parents as they go through the transitional parenthood of young children.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We want to embrace, mobilize, and transition young adults to maturity in the church's ministry and in the kingdom of God.</p>
    
